25
00:03:22,221 --> 00:03:26,216
Same as every year, do my part to help Gotham City.

26
00:03:34,219 --> 00:03:38,197
Blast! And I resolve to finally have this old clock repaired.

27
00:03:38,221 --> 00:03:41,211
