47
00:05:02,308 --> 00:05:04,322
Okay, okay, let's try this again.

48
00:05:08,317 --> 00:05:11,295
I knew it was a matter of time before you showed up.

49
00:05:11,319 --> 00:05:14,324
You try to stop me, and fail.

50
00:05:20,336 --> 00:05:22,341
Oh, yeah, that hurts.

51
00:05:24,331 --> 00:05:27,339
You try to stop me, and fail.

52
00:05:28,342 --> 00:05:30,317
Whoops! Missed me.

53
00:05:30,341 --> 00:05:33,343
Ugh. You're quicker than you look.

54
00:05:42,345 --> 00:05:44,362
Aha.

55
00:05:50,361 --> 00:05:52,344
Lights out.

56
00:05:52,368 --> 00:05:54,360
Huh?

57
00:05:55,363 --> 00:05:57,369
Ah, typical.

58
00:05:59,367 --> 00:06:01,377
Let's try this one.

59
00:06:10,378 --> 00:06:13,371
It's been a barrel of laughs, Batman.

60
00:06:13,395 --> 00:06:16,371
Oh, that's terrible.

61
00:06:16,395 --> 00:06:19,401
Better luck next time, Batman.

62
00:06:36,402 --> 00:06:39,380
'Let's look for a match.'

63
00:06:39,404 --> 00:06:41,381
I know this doesn't make sense

64
00:06:41,405 --> 00:06:43,400
but the whole thing seemed... staged.

65
00:06:43,424 --> 00:06:46,384
