184
00:16:07,972 --> 00:16:09,952
Get any sense of what he's gonna do next?

185
00:16:09,976 --> 00:16:12,993
He said he wanted Gotham to ring in the New Year with a bang.

186
00:16:14,995 --> 00:16:16,968
Tonight's New Year's Eve celebration

187
00:16:16,992 --> 00:16:18,000
in Gotham Times Square.

188
