190
00:16:23,994 --> 00:16:25,983
An evacuation would only cause panic.

191
00:16:26,007 --> 00:16:29,009
We have to find the device before it goes off.

192
00:16:34,016 --> 00:16:38,006
Wait. I have a special mission for you.

193
00:16:46,012 --> 00:16:48,005
Gotham will only understand how precious their time is

194
00:16:48,029 --> 00:16:51,001
